			as cheap and tacky or expensive and elegant.</p>

		<p class="body">Subtle touches such as careful alignment and spacing, the use of bullet points and ornamental separations between paragraphs are just some of the things that individually may not sound like much but together add up to create a stunning layout that you
			would expect from a Royal wedding.</p>


